  "reference_number": "BEL0170",
  "remarks": "\nIgor Vasilyevich KARPENKO is an involved person under the Republic of Belarus (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds:\n \nKARPENKO is and has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, and promoting:\n (1) the repression of civil society and democratic opposition in Belarus and (2) actions and activities which undermine democracy and the rule of law in Belarus. \n",
